default0
default 
defaultFor young people with long term conditions, the transition to adult health services is a difficult time. Transition needs to be built into care pathways as a process rather than a discrete event. Local leadership on improving transition is also needed, for example, through a designated transition lead in each local area and clinical champions within provider organisations.
